itative queries}.Our study is completed by a variety of\nnumerical simulations that illustrate our results and allow us to formulate\nopen questions and conjectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 16:11:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
