ion. Using huge FocalNet and DINO, we achieved 64.3 and 64.4\nmAP on COCO minival and test-dev, respectively, establishing new SoTA on top of\nmuch larger attention-based models like Swinv2-G and BEIT-3. Code and\ncheckpoints are available at https://github.com/microsoft/FocalNet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 17:54:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 09:41:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 5 Nov 2022 07:06:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
