e plasma-$\\beta$ ($\\beta_\\mathrm{m}$) remains within the range\nof 5-$10^3$, which does not impose any restriction in the simultaneous\noperation of the LSMF and the turbulent transport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 18:00:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
