rsion of time-reversal helps to clarify a recent debate\non the meaning of formal versus physical irreversibility. Extensive numerical\ncalculations based on a direct evaluation of waiting-time distributions\nillustrate our exact results and provide an estimate on the quality of the\nbounds for affinities of hidden cycles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 20:04:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 12:27:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-19"}
