 every bin\nin $O(m\\log m)$ rounds. For $m = n$, this improves the previous upper bound of\n$O(n \\log^2 n)$ in [BCNPP19]. We also prove that the upper bound is tight up to\nmultiplicative constants for any $n \\leq m \\leq \\mathrm{poly}(n)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2022 13:21:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 14:40:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
